---
title: Double One-Pot Beef Ragu & Orecchiette with Red Wine Jus, Parmesan & Parsley
description: A beef ragu needs to no introduction, it can speak for itself when it has an irresistible aroma that’s got everyone seated at your table. The secret is in the sauce, the red wine jus creates a rich flavour that goes perfectly with beef and pasta.
